  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "Idea is that within the migrations file you should be able to tell the reporter to start collecting transaction / gas data for arbitrary web3 calls (like the kind you might make while staging things around your deployments). `stopStage` would trigger the reporter to output accumulated costs & add them to the deployment totals.\r\n\r\n```javascript\r\ndeployer.emit.startStage()\r\ndeployer.emit.endStage()\r\n```\r\n",
